12
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:39,760
他们必如鹰展翅上腾
They will soar on wings like eagles.

13
00:02:39,950 --> 00:02:40,950
他们奔跑
They will run

14
00:02:41,130 --> 00:02:42,420
却不困倦
and not be weary.

15
00:02:42,580 --> 00:02:43,580
他们行走
They will walk

16
00:02:44,100 --> 00:02:45,440
却不疲乏
and not be faint.

17
