等等
Wait up.

25
00:03:17,610 --> 00:03:18,460
跟上
Catch up.

26
00:03:19,670 --> 00:03:21,790
等等 我有事要和你说
Wait up. I got something to tell you.

27
00:03:25,540 --> 00:03:26,750
哈尔 怎么了
What, Hal?

28
00:03:28,100 --> 00:03:29,290
看谁先跑到山顶
Race you to the top.

29
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:30,910
嘿 骗子
Hey, cheater!

30
00:03:40,990 --> 00:03:42,200
再见 小短腿
See you later, slowpoke.

31
00:03:42,330 --> 00:03:43,050
嘿
Hey.

32
00:03:49,940 --> 00:03:50,850
要拉你一把吗
You wanna hand?

33
00:03:51,070 --> 00:03:52,080
我能行
I got it.

34
00:03:58,670 --> 00:03:59,650
下去吧
Saved you.

35
00:03:59,670 --> 00:04:00,790
别乱动 别闹
Ah, you don't. Quit it.

36
00:04:00,820 --> 00:04:01,910
你别闹
You quit it.

37
00:04:06,200 --> 00:04:07,820
天哪
For Pete's sake.

38
00:04:08,370 --> 00:04:10,180
别站在悬崖边上
Hey, get away from that ledge.

39
00:04:10,200 --> 00:04:11,560
你们这两个愚蠢的小鬼
You damn fool kids.

40
00:04:11,590 --> 00:04:13,320
你们会摔断脖子的
You gonna break your neck.

41
00:04:15,260 --> 00:04:16,780
是道斯家的孩子
It's them. Doss kids.

42
00:04:16,860 --> 00:04:18,610
和他们爸爸一样疯
Crazy as their old man.

43
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:29,940
他们新开了块地 就在杰克逊大街拐角...
They dug up the corner of Jackson and Main...

44
00:04:32,520 --> 00:04:34,120
铺上了人行道...
Putting in the sidewalk...

45
00:04:37,450 --> 00:04:39,830
你们现在肯定都认不出了
You boys wouldn't recognize it now.

46
00:04:46,730 --> 00:04:49,450
他们可能连你们也认不出了吧
Mind you, I doubt they'll recognize you.

47
00:04:51,570 --> 00:04:54,680
我路过的时候 他们都不认识我了
They hardly know me when I walk by 'em.

48
00:04:57,260 --> 00:04:59,470
就好像我和你们一起死了
It's like I died with you.

49
00:05:05,090 --> 00:05:07,590
就好像我们从来就不曾存在过
It's like we boys never existed.

50
00:05:16,200 --> 00:05:19,280
我今天就想说这么多
Well, that's all I got for you today.

51
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:41,830
戴斯蒙德 用你的右手挡住他
Block him with your right, Desmond.

52
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:43,210
住手
Stop it.

53
00:05:43,430 --> 00:05:44,860
你们听到了吗
Do you hear me?

54
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:47,080
他们为什么要打架
What are they fighting about?

55
00:05:47,110 --> 00:05:48,670
他们打架还需要理由吗
When did they ever need a reason?

56
00:05:48,690 --> 00:05:49,800
汤姆 你就...
Hey, Tom, do you...

57
00:05:50,640 --> 00:05:52,690
为什么要管 省得我还得揍他们两个
Why stop 'em? Saves me whipping them both.

58
00:05:52,710 --> 00:05:54,900
这样我只需要揍赢的那个
This way, I'd whip the one that wins.

59
00:05:58,230 --> 00:05:59,030
汤姆
Tom.

60
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:00,140
不
No!

61
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,100
天哪
Oh God.

62
00:06:03,470 --> 00:06:04,110
汤姆
Tom!

63
00:06:04,140 --> 00:06:05,590
醒醒 能听到我说话吗
Wake up. Can you hear me?

64
00:06:05,730 --> 00:06:06,860
你他妈的做了什么
What the hell have you done?

65
00:06:06,890 --> 00:06:08,040
他没有意识了
He can't hear me.

66
00:06:08,910 --> 00:06:09,670
让我来
I got it.

67
00:06:10,780 --> 00:06:12,280
我去找些冰块
I'll get some ice.

68
00:06:15,460 --> 00:06:16,960
把篮子拿开
You shift that basket.

69
00:06:17,130 --> 00:06:18,130
我来
I got it.

70
00:06:19,350 --> 00:06:20,680
他还有呼吸吗
Is he breathing?

71
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:22,680
哈尔
Hal?

72
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:24,770
哈尔 能听见我说话吗
Hal, can you hear me?

73
00:06:29,810 --> 00:06:32,570
哈尔 能听见我说话吗
Hal, can you hear me?

74
00:06:37,500 --> 00:06:38,310
哈尔
Hal?

75
00:06:39,510 --> 00:06:40,270
醒醒
Come on.

76
00:06:40,310 --> 00:06:41,890
上帝啊 救救他吧
Dear God help him.

77
00:06:42,350 --> 00:06:43,350
哈尔
Hal...

78
00:07:05,110 --> 00:07:08,000
你知道自己在干什么吗
What do you think you doing?

79
00:07:08,880 --> 00:07:11,950
我现在要揍你了
I'm going to have to beat you now.

80
00:07:11,980 --> 00:07:14,910
你知道规矩
You know the rules.

81
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,960
你听到了吗 戴斯蒙德
You hear me, Desmond?

82
00:07:19,830 --> 00:07:20,830
戴斯蒙德
Desmond!

83
00:07:20,860 --> 00:07:22,260
汤姆 住手
Tom. Stop.

84
00:07:22,450 --> 00:07:24,150
不能这样教孩子
What's that gonna teach the boy?

85
00:07:24,170 --> 00:07:26,010
他已经够暴力的了
He's violence enough already.

86
00:07:26,630 --> 00:07:29,210
行吧 你就继续宠着他吧
Okay, fine. You go smother him in kisses.

87
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:32,710
继续告诉他 这世界是个美好善良的地方
You tell him the world is a soft and gentle place.

88
00:07:36,970 --> 00:07:39,070
哈尔会没事的
Hal's gonna be okay.

89
00:07:50,320 --> 00:07:51,080
嘿
Hey.

90
00:07:55,370 --> 00:07:56,950
我差点就杀了他
I could've killed him.

91
00:07:57,380 --> 00:07:58,710
是的 是差点
Yes, you could have.

92
00:07:59,850 --> 00:08:02,120
杀戮是最大的罪恶
Murder, it's the worst sin of all.

93
00:08:02,770 --> 00:08:04,330
而夺走另一个人的生命
And to take another man's life,

94
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:07,180
在上帝眼中 是最严重的罪恶
that is the most egregious sin in Lord's eye.

95
00:08:08,130 --> 00:08:10,180
这个最伤上帝的心
Nothing hurts His heart so much.

96
00:08:11,900 --> 00:08:14,270
- 你听不懂话吗 - 汤姆 你...
- Don't you understand English? - God konw, Tom ...

97
00:08:14,300 --> 00:08:16,660
- 难道还要我再说一次吗 - 我告诉你...
- Do I have to tell you again? - I am telling you...

98
00:08:16,750 --> 00:08:18,620
你最好自己滚 女人 否则我会给你点颜色看看
You move, woman, or I will wallop you good and hard!

99
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:20,080
到底怎么回事
What the hell is going on?

100
00:08:20,100 --> 00:08:22,160
- 你没事吧 贝莎 - 你他妈管好自己吧
- You okay, Bertha?- You mind your own damned business!

101
00:08:22,180 --> 00:08:24,180
回去睡觉吧 汤姆
Go sleep it off, Tom.

102
00:08:25,490 --> 00:08:26,950
我讨厌他
I hate him.

103
00:08:42,370 --> 00:08:43,480
妈妈
Momma?

104
00:08:56,410 --> 00:08:58,610
他为什么这么恨我们
Why does he hate us so much?

105
00:08:59,770 --> 00:09:02,400
他不恨我们
Oh, he don't hate us.

106
00:09:04,470 --> 00:09:05,800
他恨的是自己
He hates himself.

107
00:09:06,520 --> 00:09:07,910
有时候
Sometimes.

108
00:09:09,460 --> 00:09:11,730
今晚你父亲... 这不是他本来的样子
Your daddy tonight... that ain’t the real him.

109
00:09:13,330 --> 00:09:16,810
我希望你们能像我一样 认识战前的他
I wish you knew him like I did, before the war.

110
00:09:40,030 --> 00:09:41,650
我们唱得如何 戴斯蒙德
How do we sound, Desmond?

111
00:09:41,750 --> 00:09:43,810
就像是天堂里的天使 妈妈
Like a heavenly host angel, Mom.

112
00:09:44,190 --> 00:09:46,340
你知道 说谎也是种罪
Now, you know it's a sin to tell a lie,

113
00:09:46,370 --> 00:09:47,870
特别是在这里
especially in this place.

114
00:09:47,890 --> 00:09:50,160
我从来没说过 那是负责歌唱的天使
Well, I never said they were singing angels.

115
00:09:55,820 --> 00:09:57,670
外面发生了什么 戴斯蒙德
What's going on out there, Desmond?

116
00:09:57,690 --> 00:10:00,280
快 把车抬起来 把车抬起来
Go on. Get it up, get it up!

117
00:10:02,530 --> 00:10:03,310
把他拉出来
Drag him out.

118
00:10:03,330 --> 00:10:04,710
把垫子拉出来
Just the tarp.

119
00:10:09,870 --> 00:10:11,140
我去叫救护车
I'll phone an ambulance.

120
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:12,320
不 没时间了
No, no time.

121
00:10:12,400 --> 00:10:13,370
约书亚 你的皮卡呢
Joshua, your pick-up?

122
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:13,900
快去
Quick!

123
00:10:13,930 --> 00:10:14,820
好的
Okay.

124
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:34,330
- 你会没事的 - 你会没事的
- You're going to be fine now. - You're going to be fine.

125
00:10:34,650 --> 00:10:36,020
有人在照顾你
You're in good hands.

126
00:10:38,220 --> 00:10:39,550
他怎么了
What have we got here?

127
00:10:39,690 --> 00:10:40,590
主动脉破裂
That's a severed artery.

128
00:10:40,620 --> 00:10:41,820
- 准备缝合 - 好的 医生
- Get some sutures.- Yes, doctor.

129
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:43,010
压住伤口
Put some pressure on it.

130
00:10:43,040 --> 00:10:44,210
这根止血带是你绑的吗
Did you apply this tourniquet?

131
00:10:44,230 --> 00:10:44,980
是的 先生
Yes, sir.

132
00:10:45,010 --> 00:10:47,260
干得好 你也许救了这孩子的命
Nice work. You might've saved this boy's life.

133
00:10:48,430 --> 00:10:50,510
有我们陪着你 你会没事的
You're staying with us. You're going to be okay.

134
00:10:51,020 --> 00:10:51,860
我们可以搞定
We can get that.

135
00:10:51,890 --> 00:10:52,900
你叫什么 孩子
What's your name, son?

136
00:10:52,930 --> 00:10:53,930
吉尔伯特
Gilbert.

137
00:10:54,940 --> 00:10:56,550
- 需要手术吗 - 没错 需要手术
- Surgery? - Yeah, Surgery.

138
00:10:56,690 --> 00:10:58,690
保持清醒 你会没事的
Stay with us, you're gonna be okay.

139
00:10:59,510 --> 00:11:00,510
你感觉疼吗
You feel pain?

140
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:01,600
当然了 医生
Certainly, doc.

141
00:11:04,160 --> 00:11:06,370
保持清醒 好吗
Stay with us, okay?

142
00:12:05,220 --> 00:12:07,890
军队体测在那边 这里是献血处
Army physical is that way. This is for giving blood.

143
00:12:14,050 --> 00:12:15,180
你没事吧
Are you alright?

144
00:12:17,060 --> 00:12:18,840
没事 那不是我的血
Oh no. That's not mine.

145
00:12:19,500 --> 00:12:20,500
我没事
I'm fine.

146
00:12:21,110 --> 00:12:22,670
谢谢关心 女士
Thank you for asking, though, ma'am.

147
00:12:27,460 --> 00:12:28,850
你需要什么吗
What do you need?

148
00:12:31,380 --> 00:12:32,520
我的皮带
My belt.

149
00:12:35,830 --> 00:12:38,540
我借给出事的那个小伙子了
I lend it to the boy who had the accident.

150
00:12:38,570 --> 00:12:41,290
没有皮带 我的裤子会往下掉
My pants don't hold up so good without it.

151
00:12:42,360 --> 00:12:45,130
好吧 我没有你的皮带
Well, I don't have your belt.

152
00:12:45,150 --> 00:12:46,080
不 我知道 女士
No. I know that, ma'am.

153
00:12:46,110 --> 00:12:48,630
皮带在外面 还在那个小伙子腿上
It's out there, right out there with the boy still.

154
00:12:48,810 --> 00:12:49,810
好吧
Okay.

155
00:12:50,530 --> 00:12:52,710
我只是在这里负责采血
I'm just here to take blood.

156
00:12:52,910 --> 00:12:54,350
我来献血吧
I'll give you mine.

157
00:12:55,740 --> 00:12:56,740
好吧
Okay,

158
00:12:56,830 --> 00:12:58,860
去那间屋子里 和其他人一起等着
go to that room over there and wait with the others.

159
00:12:58,880 --> 00:13:00,150
我会叫你
I'll call you.

160
00:13:05,270 --> 00:13:06,330
那个... 房间
That... that room.

161
00:13:14,860 --> 00:13:17,700
你之前献过血吗
You've ever given blood before, Mr....

162
00:13:19,050 --> 00:13:20,050
道斯
Doss.

163
00:13:21,460 --> 00:13:22,590
但我的朋友都叫我戴斯蒙德
But my friends call me Desmond.

164
00:13:22,620 --> 00:13:24,460
没有 女士 这是第一次献血
No, ma'am. My first time.

165
00:13:32,940 --> 00:13:35,750
我的梦想是当一名医生 但...
I always dream about being a doctor but...

166
00:13:36,970 --> 00:13:38,510
我没怎么上过学
I didn't get much school.

167
00:13:40,670 --> 00:13:43,000
献完了血 你可能会有点头晕
You might be a little dizzy when we're done.

168
00:13:43,540 --> 00:13:45,140
有人会来接你吗
Is somebody picking you up?

169
00:13:46,030 --> 00:13:47,830
不 女士 我打算走回去
No, ma'am. Walking back.

170
00:13:48,400 --> 00:13:49,600
你住在哪里呢
Where do you live?

171
00:13:50,290 --> 00:13:51,490
希尔堡 女士
Fort Hill, ma'am.

172
00:13:52,080 --> 00:13:52,990
那很远啊
That's a ways.

173
00:13:53,010 --> 00:13:55,380
不远 也就五六英里吧
No. Just five or six miles,

174
00:13:55,850 --> 00:13:57,450
如果我从树林走回去
but I cut through the woods.

175
00:13:58,080 --> 00:13:59,380
那就是七英里
It's seven that way!

176
00:14:00,370 --> 00:14:01,670
你肯定很喜欢树林吧
You must really like the woods.

177
00:14:01,700 --> 00:14:03,470
是的 女士 当然
Yes, ma'am. Sure do.

178
00:14:04,400 --> 00:14:04,990
好吧
Okay.

179
00:14:05,010 --> 00:14:06,770
用力按住这里
Put some pressure here.

180
00:14:08,030 --> 00:14:09,030
你没事吧
You okay?

181
00:14:09,240 --> 00:14:10,210
没事
Yeah.

182
00:14:14,570 --> 00:14:17,870
你穿得这么帅 要去哪里啊
Where are you going looking all spruced and nice?

183
00:14:17,950 --> 00:14:19,480
昨天遇见了一个人
Met someone yesterday.

184
00:14:19,910 --> 00:14:20,930
一个在医院的护士
A nurse over at the hospital.

185
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:22,690
她叫多萝西·舒特 我要娶她
Her name's Dorothy Schutte, and I'm gonna marry her.

186
00:14:22,710 --> 00:14:24,430
天哪 她知道吗
Goodness, does she know that?

187
00:14:24,460 --> 00:14:26,180
还不知道 但她会知道的
Well, not yet. She's about to.

188
00:14:26,640 --> 00:14:28,600
你和女人说过话吗
You've ever even spoken to a woman?

189
00:14:28,620 --> 00:14:30,840
我的意思是 除了家人以外的女人
I mean, one that's not family.

190
00:14:30,940 --> 00:14:31,940
我和她说过话了
Spoke to her.

191
00:14:33,280 --> 00:14:36,150
既然那样 来和你哥哥抱一个
Well, in that case, come and give your brother a big hug.

192
00:14:36,180 --> 00:14:38,670
- 来吧 - 不要用你的脏手碰我
- Come here. - Keep your greasy paws off me.

193
00:14:40,230 --> 00:14:41,430
祝我好运 妈妈
Wish me luck, momma.

194
00:14:42,180 --> 00:14:43,410
祝你好运
Good luck.

195
00:15:20,380 --> 00:15:21,380
下一个
Next.

196
00:15:21,800 --> 00:15:22,800
坐吧
Grab a seat.

197
00:15:23,310 --> 00:15:24,870
您之前献过血吗
You've ever given blood before?

