我可没那么说
I didn't say that.

218
00:16:28,270 --> 00:16:31,330
动脉和静脉的区别是什么
What's the difference between an artery and a vein?

219
00:16:33,320 --> 00:16:34,850
你在说什么
What are you talking about?

220
00:16:34,870 --> 00:16:36,580
那个男孩的事故
The boy's accident.

221
00:16:38,910 --> 00:16:40,830
动脉的血是喷出来的
Arteries spurt blood.

222
00:16:42,350 --> 00:16:43,350
静脉呢
And veins?

223
00:16:45,200 --> 00:16:46,200
流出来的
Bleed.

224
00:16:49,430 --> 00:16:50,580
我觉得 你应该在出门前
I think you need to practice your

225
00:16:50,610 --> 00:16:53,350
好好练习下 如何和女生聊天
boy-girl-dating-talk at home before you come out.

226
00:16:53,760 --> 00:16:55,280
没错 我确实需要练习
Yeah, I probably do.

227
00:16:57,140 --> 00:16:59,880
如果你感兴趣 我可以给你一本书
I'll give you a book if you're that interested.

228
00:17:01,230 --> 00:17:02,290
关于约会的吗
On dating?

229
00:17:04,110 --> 00:17:05,260
关于血液的
On blood.

230
00:17:13,700 --> 00:17:15,960
还有什么医学问题吗
Another medical question perhaps?

231
00:17:16,470 --> 00:17:20,200
不 我觉得 你是我见过最漂亮的姑娘
No. I just think you're the prettiest thing I've ever seen.

232
00:17:21,250 --> 00:17:23,580
因为我坐在暗处 你看不清楚
That's because I'm sitting in the dark.

233
00:17:26,450 --> 00:17:27,020
不
No.

234
00:17:29,030 --> 00:17:30,430
你真是太美了
You're just beautiful.

235
00:17:55,370 --> 00:17:57,230
别挡道
Out of the way!

236
00:17:58,720 --> 00:18:01,100
你走路得看着前面
You need to watch where you're going.

237
00:18:12,940 --> 00:18:15,210
抱歉 我以为你不介意
I'm sorry. I didn't think you'd mind.

238
00:18:15,670 --> 00:18:17,000
你又没问
You didn't ask.

239
00:18:18,040 --> 00:18:19,640
我以为你会接受
I thought you might've liked it.

240
00:18:19,660 --> 00:18:21,720
你要是问了 我说不定会接受
Well, I might've if you'd asked.

241
00:18:32,500 --> 00:18:33,500
你要来吗
You coming?

242
00:18:36,260 --> 00:18:38,120
走路看着点
Watch where you're walking!

243
