everytime I walk to my bed?

372
00:28:03,130 --> 00:28:05,500
看吧 看吧 你就嫉妒吧 朋友
Gaze upon it in envy, my friend.

373
00:28:06,910 --> 00:28:07,910
你还好吗
You okay there?

374
00:28:08,330 --> 00:28:09,330
你看起来是迷路了
You look lost.

375
00:28:09,450 --> 00:28:10,990
这里有个空床
Vacancy right here.

376
00:28:11,620 --> 00:28:12,620
明智的选择
Wise choice.

377
00:28:12,880 --> 00:28:15,280
这可是依山傍水的好位置
It's got views of the mountains down to lake.

378
00:28:15,540 --> 00:28:16,540
我是兰德尔·富勒
Randall Fuller.

379
00:28:18,100 --> 00:28:19,100
我是戴斯蒙德·道斯
Desmond Doss.

380
00:28:19,290 --> 00:28:20,420
叫他"老师"吧
Call him 'Teach'.

381
00:28:20,840 --> 00:28:22,350
他说的话 别人都听不懂
No one understand a word he says.

382
00:28:22,410 --> 00:28:24,450
那是因为这里其他人都不读书
That's because no one else here can read.

383
00:28:24,540 --> 00:28:26,210
不过那对蛋蛋的主人
The testicles there belong to a man

384
