02:02:32,100 --> 02:02:33,700
道斯二等兵正在为你们祈祷
Private Doss is praying for you?

1681
02:02:33,730 --> 02:02:35,760
他妈的谁是道斯二等兵
Who the hell is Private Doss?

1682
02:02:57,640 --> 02:02:58,770
准备出发
Let's go to work.

1683
02:04:51,690 --> 02:04:52,560
跪下
Down!

1684
02:04:52,580 --> 02:04:55,810
跪下 跪在地上
Get down! Get down on the ground!

1685
02:04:55,830 --> 02:04:57,560
立刻跪下
On the ground. Now!

1686
02:05:36,970 --> 02:05:39,490
躺下 快躺下 我有吗啡
Lay down! Lay down! Lay down! I got the morphine.

1687
02:05:40,860 --> 02:05:42,720
快走 快走 快带他离开这里
Let's go! Let's go. Let's get this man outta here.

1688
02:05:42,740 --> 02:05:43,740
快 快
Go! Go!

1689
02:05:48,410 --> 02:05:49,410
我的《圣经》
My Bible...

1690
02:05:49,830 --> 02:05:52,420
我的《圣经》 我的《圣经》
My Bible. My Bible...

1691
02:05:52,450 --> 02:05:54,960
停 停 快停下
Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop!

1692
02:05:55,140 --> 02:05:58,790
我的《圣经》 我的《圣经》
My Bible. My Bible.

1693
02:05:59,360 --> 02:06:00,360
知道了
Okay.

1694
02:07:15,940 --> 02:07:17,480
戴斯蒙德 你马上就能回家了
You going home, Desmond.

1695
02:07:17,930 --> 02:07:19,530
我们拿下了钢锯岭
We've taken the Hacksaw.

1696
02:07:23,870 --> 02:07:26,160
等等 等等 戴斯蒙德
Hold up! Hold up! Desmond.

1697
02:07:28,310 --> 02:07:29,310
戴斯蒙德
Desmond.

1698
02:09:16,360 --> 02:09:18,820
当时 我一直在祈祷
I was praying the whole time.

1699
02:09:19,600 --> 02:09:20,790
我一直向主祈祷
I just kept praying,

1700
02:09:20,810 --> 02:09:23,820
"主啊 求求你 让我再救一个吧"
"Lord, please help me get one more."

1701
02:09:24,840 --> 02:09:25,720
每当救下一个人之后
When I got this,

1702
02:09:25,750 --> 02:09:29,440
我就继续祈祷 "主啊 求你 让我再救一个吧"
I said "Lord, please help me get one more".

1703
02:09:35,990 --> 02:09:37,810
在我看来
I would say anyone is wrong

1704
02:09:37,830 --> 02:09:40,090
试图改变任何人的信仰 都是不明智的
to try to compromise somebody's conviction.

1705
02:09:40,110 --> 02:09:43,210
不论是在军队 还是在其他地方
I don't care whether it's the army or what it is.

1706
02:09:43,720 --> 02:09:45,530
只要你秉承自己的信仰
When you're on a conviction,

1707
02:09:46,230 --> 02:09:47,490
那就绝不是玩笑
that is not a joke.

1708
02:09:49,570 --> 02:09:50,900
而是真正的你
That's what you are.

1709
02:09:52,660 --> 02:09:54,130
虽然我对他说了许多
Even though I said those things

1710
02:09:54,150 --> 02:09:56,410
说他应该拿枪上战场
to him in regard to carrying a rifle,

1711
02:09:56,710 --> 02:09:58,730
如果他不拿枪
then... then he would never be my...

1712
02:09:58,760 --> 02:10:02,650
我就绝不会和他一起并肩作战
by my damn side at all unless he had a rifle.

1713
02:10:03,120 --> 02:10:05,600
但最终
But then, in the long run,

1714
02:10:05,860 --> 02:10:10,170
我却发现 他是最英勇的士兵之一
finding out that he was one of the bravest persons alive.

1715
02:10:10,820 --> 02:10:12,280
而最后 还需要他来救我
And then to have him ended up

1716
02:10:12,300 --> 02:10:16,330
这简直太讽刺了
saving my life was the irony of the whole thing.

1717
02:10:16,790 --> 02:10:21,230
鲜血从他的脸庞和眼睛上流下
Blood had ran down through to the fella's face and eyes.

1718
02:10:22,250 --> 02:10:25,900
当时 他躺在那里 呻吟着 不停地叫医护兵
He was laying there just groaning and calling for a medic.

1719
02:10:27,560 --> 02:10:31,450
我从水壶中倒了些水 拿了些纱布
I took the water from my canteen and got some bandages,

1720
02:10:31,650 --> 02:10:33,890
帮他洗了脸
and I washed his face.

1721
02:10:34,760 --> 02:10:36,510
当他眼里的鲜血 被擦干净之后
And when I was washing his eyes,

1722
02:10:36,980 --> 02:10:39,310
他睁开了眼睛
his eyes came up.

1723
02:10:39,330 --> 02:10:42,500
他简直高兴坏了
Man, he just lit up.

1724
02:10:44,170 --> 02:10:47,050
他说 "我还以为我瞎了"
He says "I thought I was blind."

1725
02:10:48,410 --> 02:10:51,220
而当时他脸上的笑容
And if I hadn't got anything more out of the war

1726
02:10:51,240 --> 02:10:53,310
对我而言
than that smile he gave me,

1727
02:10:53,490 --> 02:10:56,580
就是最好的回报
I wouldn't have been well repaid.

